data.description: Well maintained home in Eaglesmere.  Home features 3 large bedrooms and a great loft area for convenient use as an office, extra den or whatever great use of the space you can imagine.  Partially finished basement has a full bath for easy access for guests when entertaining and a large storage area. New vinyl plank floors throughout main level.  Roof replaced less than a year ago. Kitchen features a pantry and 42 inch cabinets and a nice island for extra seating that sits in front of the breakfast nook overlooking the back yard.  Small deck off of the kitchen leads to the fenced yard which has separate sections for pets and a garden. Don't miss out on this one. Professional Pictures to follow soon
